name: Findingyourotherhalf
0:
”Alexa, ask love forecast who is my other half?”
”Alexa, ask love forecast who is my true love?”
”Alexa, ask love forecast who is my future girlfriend?”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: love forecast
des:
This skill allows Alexa to search for your "True Love."
She will tell you information such as occupation, age, blood type, and etc. of your other half.


This is a simple custom skill, and no prerequisites are required for this skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
